msgstr "Aros, beth oedd yn bod?"

msgid "You again?!"
msgstr "Chi eto?!"

msgid "Something is supposed to happen here, but it's not in this version so check back later!"
msgstr "Rhywbeth i fod i ddigwydd yma, ond nid yn y fersiwn hwn felly gofynnwch yn ôl yn ddiweddarach!"

msgid "Have fun!"
msgstr "Cael hwyl!"

msgid "Thanks for resucing my chickens, have you got me 2 logs from the forest yet?"
msgstr "Diolch am fy resucing ieir, ydych chi wedi 'm 2 o'r cofnodion y goedwig eto?"

msgid "Thanks Edgar! My chickens are back and these logs will do me fine"
msgstr "Edgar Diolch! Fy ieir yn ôl a bydd y rhain goed braf i mi ei wneud"

msgid "Take this sword, may it serve you well!"
msgstr "Gall Cymerwch y cleddyf, mae'n gwasanaethu chi hefyd!"

msgid "Thank you!"
msgstr "Ddiolch 'ch!"

msgid "Thanks for the logs, have you had any luck with the chickens?"
msgstr "Diolch am y logiau, a ydych wedi cael unrhyw lwc gyda'r ieir?"

msgid "I'll give you a sword if you get me 2 chopped logs from the forest and rescue at least 3 of my chickens"
msgstr "'N annhymerus' anrhega 'ch cleddyf os ydych yn cael' m 2 logiau torri o'r goedwig ac achub o leiaf 3 o fy ieir"

msgid "Hello Edgar, what can I do for you today?"
msgstr "Hello Edgar, beth gallaf ei wneud i chi heddiw?"

msgid "Do you have a sword I can borrow?"
msgstr "Oes gennych chi cleddyf gallaf fenthyg?"

msgid "I do have a sword and you can have it if you do something for me first"
msgstr "Oes gennyf chleddyf a gallwch ei gael os ydych yn gwneud rhywbeth i mi yn gyntaf"

msgid "OK... what do I have to do?"
msgstr "OK ... beth mae'n rhaid i mi ei wneud?"

msgid "Some of my chickens have escaped from their pen and I would be very grateful if you can get them back for me"
msgstr "Mae rhai o fy ieir wedi dianc o'r eu pen, a byddwn yn ddiolchgar iawn os y gallwch eu cael yn ôl i mi"

msgid "I have set up some traps near their pen, you can lure them to the traps using this chicken feed. I don't need them all, but at least 3 would be very helpful. I can get the rest myself."
msgstr "Rwyf wedi sefydlu rhai trapiau ger eu pen, gallwch eu denu i ddefnyddio trapiau hyn yn bwydo i cyw iâr. Nid oes angen i bob un ohonynt, ond o leiaf 3 byddai yn ddefnyddiol iawn. Alla i gael y gweddill fy hun."

msgid "That's it?"
msgstr "Dyna 'i?"

msgid "Not quite. Can you also get me some wood from the forest? 2 logs should be sufficient"
msgstr "Nid eithaf. Gallwch hefyd gael i mi rhai pren o'r goedwig? 2 Dylai cofnodion fod yn ddigon"

msgid "Do you have an axe?"
msgstr "Oes gennych chi bwyell?"

