msgstr "ERM ... I mi adael fy bwyell yn y goedwig yn rhywle. Dylai fod yn dal i fod yno"

msgid "Isn't that forest dangerous?"
msgstr "Yw nad yw coedwig beryglus?"

msgid "Not really, if anything gets in your way, just hit it with a weapon"
msgstr "Nid mewn gwirionedd, os oes unrhyw beth yn cael yn eich ffordd, jyst daro â arf"

msgid "Such as an axe?"
msgstr "O'r fath fel bwyell?"

msgid "Yes, that would do the trick"
msgstr "Ie, a fyddai'n gwneud y gamp"

msgid "..."
msgstr "..."

msgid "But seriously, there's nothing in there that can really harm you. That problem was dealt with a long time ago..."
msgstr "Ond o ddifrif, does dim byd yno sy'n gallu niweidio chi mewn gwirionedd. Y broblem yn ymdrin â amser maith yn ôl ..."

msgid "Good luck!"
msgstr "Good luck!"

msgid "Oh, thanks Edgar, I only needed 3, but thanks for the additional help!"
msgstr "O, diolch Edgar, yr wyf yn unig angen 3, ond diolch am yr help ychwanegol!"

msgid "Here, Maggie made me this health potion but I don't need it so why don't you have it?"
msgstr "Yma, Maggie yn gwneud i mi hwn potion iechyd ond dwi ddim yn angen, felly pam na wnewch chi ei gael?"

