msgid "What was that?"
msgstr "Beth oedd hynny?"

msgid "Uh Oh..."
msgstr "UH O ..."

msgid "Phew, I'm glad to be out of there"
msgstr "Phew, rwy'n falch o fod allan o yno"

msgid "Now to get through this swamp"
msgstr "Nawr i gael drwy'r gors"

msgid "Hey, what's this?"
msgstr "Hey, beth yw hwn?"

msgid "Looks pretty harmless, I'll try stepping on it"
msgstr "Yn edrych yn eithaf diniwed, 'n annhymerus' brofi camu ar ei"

msgid "Wow! That was cool! This must be a mechanical teleporter."
msgstr "Wow! Dyna oedd cŵl! Rhaid i hyn fod yn teleporter mecanyddol."

msgid "I wonder if it works both ways..."
msgstr "Tybed os yw'n gweithio ddwy ffordd ..."

msgid "Horray!"
msgstr "Horray!"

msgid "Not only is this going to save me a lot of walking, it's also loads of fun!"
msgstr "Nid yn unig yw hyn yn mynd i mi arbed llawer o gerdded, mae hefyd yn llawer o hwyl!"

msgid "Now try out your shield"
msgstr "Nawr ceisiwch eich darian"

msgid "Block the pellets spat out by the plant and jump up to the next ledge"
msgstr "Bloc y pelenni spat gan y planhigyn a naid hyd at y ysgafell nesaf"

